            SIREN/SIRET: — VAT: [Number, if applicable]<br>
            Contact: contact@aicebergmind.com<br>
            Last updated: 6th August 2025
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Introduction</h2>
