            Unless otherwise stated, all content on the Site (texts, graphics, logos, videos, audio, design, software/source code) is owned by AIceberg Mind or its licensors and protected by applicable IP laws. Third-party trademarks and content are the property of their respective owners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">License and Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            AIceberg Mind grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to access and use the Site for personal, non-commercial purposes. Prohibited uses include unauthorized copying, distribution, or modification of content.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Links and Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            You may link to public pages of the Site provided the link is fair and lawful, does not damage our reputation or suggest endorsement, and does not frame our content. We may request removal of links at our discretion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Disclaimers and Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            The Site is provided “as is” and “as available,” without warranties of any kind, express or implied, including merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            AIceberg Mind acts as the data controller for personal data processed through the Site. Contact: contact@aicebergmind.com. Data Protection Officer: No DPO designated.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            We use cookies and similar technologies to operate the Site, measure audiences, and personalize content. Non-essential cookies are used only with your consent via our cookie banner.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            These Terms are governed by French law and applicable EU legislation. Competent courts in France shall have jurisdiction, without prejudice to mandatory protections applicable to consumers in their country of residence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Contact</h2>
          <p class="editorial-body">
            For inquiries, please contact us at contact@aicebergmind.com.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>